<div class="jumbotron text-center">
  <div class="container">
    <a href="/" class="lang-logo">
      <img src="/assets/logo.png">
    </a>
    <h1>Getting Started with Storj on Heroku</h1>
    <p>Storj object storage provider, allowing application developers to store their data quickly, securely, and for half the price.</p>
    <a type="button" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="http://docs.storj.io/">Getting Started with Storj</a>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="alert alert-success text-center" role="alert">
    <a href="#" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="close" title="close">Ã—</a>
    Your Storj email is: <strong><%= STORJ_EMAIL %></strong><br>
